CodeTyphon/39_Goto.html.body:
Goto 语句Goto 语句
语法
goto label;
   ...
   ...
label: statement;
流程图

官方样例
program exGoto;
label 1; 
var
   a : integer;
begin
   a :=10;
   (* repeat until loop execution *)
   1: repeat
      if( a =15 )then
      begin
         (* skip the iteration *)
         a := a + 1;
         goto 1;
      end;
      writeln('value of a: ', a);
      a:= a + 1;
   until a = 20;
end.

